Package: data.bls.gov
Title: Bureau of Labor Statistics API v2 Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the BLS API v2. Fetch CPI, unemployment,
    payrolls, PPI, JOLTS, and any BLS series by ID. Convenience wrappers for
    major economic indicators. Auto-chunks large series requests.
